{"tid":1808057,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"呢單無人講？公屋夫婦 藏10槍86發子彈被捕","createTime":"2020-01-02T06:32:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-02T07:21:37.000Z","uid":262063,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"068121f7729af73391fce23266804853a3f6a77b","tid":1808057,"uid":262063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T06:32:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20200102/60441482?utm_campaign=hkad_social_applecitycrime&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20200102%2F60441482%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_applecitycrime%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=lD%2FUaJpd7HswZ4lFnFCcPhx0icFY2nnrImD0qQ%2FuO9w%3D&h=180a7ed0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20200102%2F60441482%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_applecitycrime%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=a82d7ab2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20200102/60441482?utm_campaign=hkad_social_applecitycrime&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a><br />\n<br />\n警方稱，昨晚10時許接獲報案，指深水埗麗閣邨麗芙樓一單位內藏有一批槍械。警員趕至現場，在單位內發現6支懷疑曲尺手槍、4支懷疑左輪手槍、86發子彈及一副手扣，將屋內一對夫婦帶署扣查。<br />\n<br />\n涉事夫婦姓梁及姓何（62歲及61歲）涉嫌無牌管有槍械或彈藥、藏有攻擊性武器及藏有仿製槍械被捕。警方稍後將該批手槍及子彈作進一步檢驗，案件交由深水埗警區刑事調查隊跟進。<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;-<br />\n遊行前起到，就話打算遊行時用<br />\n遊行後起到，又可以點作？<br />\n先後幾次起到槍，點解都未有黑警出事？<br />\n冚住左？<br />\n定未突破到心理關口？怕民意逆轉？<br />\n<br />\n好多疑問<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但可以肯定<br />\n日日睇住黑警殘暴過日軍嘅暴行<br />\n迫香港人變勇武<br />\n真.香港人對武力反抗接受嘅程度只會愈來愈高<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果真係有手足咁大風險行呢步<br />\n離核爆仲好遠<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">不割！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n只希望手足們平安<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3e2327fc3b7f082ec28a59f932b77363dba7009","tid":1808057,"uid":27432,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T06:33:59.000Z","msg":"應該係手足, 既親人?<br />\n手足死左, 而家滅口?"},{"pid":"f608f2384728de12e79f0787b5bb92ffdd8657a8","tid":1808057,"uid":17397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T06:34:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6236c7bf886a658e225e3ef9ef3bd093e66a77cf","tid":1808057,"uid":102700,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T06:35:01.000Z","msg":"香港咁易有槍但係都冇拎過黎用?<br />\n我真係唔係幾明"},{"pid":"e74461dc94e8eedb0f439c0c5bc3c7db98d75a58","tid":1808057,"uid":109629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T06:35:46.000Z","msg":"應該係銀髮族手足提供文具俾小朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cc2a5d4d89ad383dce4cdbe22bf336cc1196fff","tid":1808057,"uid":4957,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T06:36:09.000Z","msg":"61歲都勇武過你班軍師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65065d8668c1299596f967c6000d94de8ed5a0ff","tid":1808057,"uid":73856,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T06:37:18.000Z","msg":"人就拉左 野就任佢講"},{"pid":"04d84532bc00afe394cc41a5dc08d3c649362bc0","tid":1808057,"uid":240374,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T06:37:55.000Z","msg":"希望下一次新聞係<br />\n黑警被槍殺，全港市民狂慶三日三夜"},{"pid":"5a8d27830bd8230e04adfcd1e82c667069c78406","tid":1808057,"uid":997,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"6236c7bf886a658e225e3ef9ef3bd093e66a77cf","tid":1808057,"uid":102700,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T06:35:01.000Z","msg":"香港咁易有槍但